file.name: securitySchemes_insecure-test.yml
file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: API
  version: 1.0.0
  description: |
    This is a sample server Petstore server.
  termsOfService: http://swagger.io/terms/
  contact:
    email: robipolli@gmail.com
paths: {}
tags: []
servers: []
components:
  securitySchemes:
    ko_api_key_cookie:
      type: apiKey
      name: X-Api-Key
      in: cookie
    ok_api_key_header:
      type: apiKey
      name: X-Api-Key
      in: header
    ko_insecure_scheme:
      type: http
      scheme: negotiate
    ko_insecure_oauth1:
      type: http
      scheme: oauth
    ok_scheme:
      type: http
      scheme: basic
